  "conditionals": 87,
  "description": "DNA replication in Saccharomyces cerevisiae is a highly regulated process ensuring accurate genome duplication once per cell cycle. It involves origin licensing by MCM2-7 loading in G1 phase, origin firing activation by DDK and S-CDK kinases in S phase, bidirectional replication fork progression with coordinated leading and lagging strand synthesis, and completion with fork convergence and termination.",
  "id": "yeast_dna_replication",
  "logicGates": {
    "and": 5,
    "not": 5,
    "or": 5
  },
  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    %% Cell Cycle Signals\n    A[G1 Phase Entry] --> B[Low CDK Activity]\n    C[Origin Recognition] --> D[ORC Binding to ARS]\n    \n    B --> E{AND: Low CDK +<br/>ORC at Origins?}\n    D --> E\n    \n    E -->|Yes| F[Origin Licensing]\n    E -->|No| G[Wait for Conditions]\n    \n    %% MCM Loading (Licensing)\n    F --> H[ORC1-6 Complex at ARS]\n    H --> I[Cdc6 Recruitment]\n    I --> J[Cdt1 Recruitment]\n    J --> K{AND: Cdc6 + Cdt1 +<br/>ORC Present?}\n    \n    K -->|Yes| L[MCM2-7 Helicase Loading]\n    L --> M[First MCM2-7 Complex Loaded]\n    M --> N[Second MCM2-7 Complex Loaded]\n    N --> O[Pre-Replicative Complex Pre-RC]\n    \n    %% S Phase Entry\n    O --> P[S Phase Begins]\n    P --> Q[Rising CDK Activity]\n    Q --> R[S-CDK Clb5/Clb6-Cdk1]\n    \n    R --> S[DDK Dbf4-Cdc7 Kinase]\n    S --> T{AND: S-CDK + DDK<br/>Active?}\n    R --> T\n    \n    T -->|Yes| U[Origin Firing]\n    T -->|No| V[Origins Remain Licensed]\n    \n    %% Origin Activation\n    U --> W[MCM2-7 Phosphorylation by DDK]\n    W --> X[Cdc45 Recruitment]\n    U --> Y[Sld2/Sld3 Phosphorylation by S-CDK]\n    Y --> Z[Dpb11 Recruitment]\n    \n    X --> AA{AND: Cdc45 + GINS +<br/>MCM2-7?}\n    Z --> AB[GINS Complex Recruitment]\n    AB --> AA\n    \n    AA -->|Yes| AC[CMG Helicase Assembly]\n    AC --> AD[Active Replicative Helicase]\n    AD --> AE[DNA Unwinding Begins]\n    \n    %% Replication Fork Assembly\n    AE --> AF[ssDNA Exposure]\n    AF --> AG[RPA Coating ssDNA]\n    AG --> AH[DNA Polymerase \u03b1-Primase Recruitment]\n    AH --> AI[Primer Synthesis]\n    \n    AI --> AJ{OR: Leading or<br/>Lagging Strand?}\n    \n    %% Leading Strand Synthesis\n    AJ -->|Leading| AK[DNA Polymerase \u03b5 Pol2]\n    AK --> AL[Continuous Synthesis 5'\u21923']\n    AL --> AM[PCNA Clamp RFC Loading]\n    AM --> AN[Processive Leading Strand]\n    \n    %% Lagging Strand Synthesis\n    AJ -->|Lagging| AO[DNA Polymerase \u03b4 Pol3]\n    AO --> AP[Okazaki Fragment Synthesis]\n    AP --> AQ[~150 bp Fragments]\n    \n    AQ --> AR[RNA Primer + DNA]\n    AR --> AS[RNase H1 Removes Primers]\n    AS --> AT[DNA Polymerase \u03b4 Fill-In]\n    AT --> AU[DNA Ligase I Cdc9]\n    AU --> AV[Okazaki Fragment Ligation]\n    \n    %% Fork Progression\n    AN --> AW[Replication Fork Movement]\n    AV --> AW\n    AW --> AX[MCM Helicase Unwinds DNA]\n    AX --> AY{Obstacles in Path?}\n    \n    AY -->|Nucleosomes| AZ[Histone Chaperones ASF1/CAF-1]\n    AZ --> BA[Nucleosome Disassembly/Assembly]\n    BA --> AW\n    \n    AY -->|DNA Damage| BB[Fork Stalling]\n    BB --> BC[Checkpoint Activation Mec1]\n    BC --> BD[Fork Stabilization]\n    BD --> BE[Wait for Repair]\n    BE --> AW\n    \n    AY -->|Clear| AW\n    \n    %% Bidirectional Replication\n    U --> BF{OR: Early or<br/>Late Origin?}\n    BF -->|Early| BG[Fire in Early S]\n    BF -->|Late| BH[Fire in Late S]\n    BG --> AC\n    BH --> BI[Wait for Timing Program]\n    BI --> AC\n    \n    %% Preventing Re-Replication\n    Q --> BJ[/Cdc6 Degradation/]\n    BJ --> BK[/Block Re-Licensing/]\n    Q --> BL[/Cdt1 Degradation/]\n    BL --> BK\n    Q --> BM[MCM Export from Nucleus]\n    BM --> BK\n    \n    BK --> BN[Ensure Once-Per-Cell-Cycle]\n    \n    %% Fork Convergence\n    AW --> BO{Converging<br/>Forks?}\n    BO -->|Yes| BP[/Fork Termination/]\n    BO -->|No| AW\n    \n    BP --> BQ[CMG Helicase Removal]\n    BQ --> BR[Final Gap Filling]\n    BR --> BS[Nick Ligation]\n    BS --> BT[Replication Complete]\n    \n    %% Checkpoint Regulation\n    AF --> BU{Unreplicated<br/>DNA?}\n    BU -->|Yes| BV[Intra-S Checkpoint]\n    BV --> BW[Rad53 Activation]\n    BW --> BX[Slow Fork Progression]\n    BX --> BY[/Prevent Mitosis/]\n    \n    BU -->|No| BZ[S Phase Completion]\n    BZ --> CA[Enter G2 Phase]\n    \n    %% dNTP Supply\n    P --> CB[Ribonucleotide Reductase RNR]\n    CB --> CC[dNTP Synthesis]\n    CC --> CD[dNTP Pool Available]\n    CD --> AK\n    CD --> AO\n    \n    %% Quality Control\n    AL --> CE{Mismatch<br/>Detected?}\n    AP --> CE\n    \n    CE -->|Yes| CF[DNA Polymerase Exonuclease]\n    CF --> CG[Proofreading 3'\u21925']\n    CG --> CH[Error Correction]\n    CH --> AW\n    \n    CE -->|No| AW\n    \n    %% Final Outputs\n    BT --> CI[Two Identical DNA Molecules]\n    CA --> CJ[Ready for Mitosis]\n    BY --> CK[Cell Cycle Arrest if Problems]\n    \n    %% Styles\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style G fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style H fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style K fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style M fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style N fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style O fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style P fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Q fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style R fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style S fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style T fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style W fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style X fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Y fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style Z fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AA fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AB fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AC fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AD fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AE fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AF fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AH fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AI fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AJ fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AK fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AL fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AM fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AN fill:#b3e5fc,col